<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَخَرَاجٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَعُشْرِ تِجَارَةٍ مِنَ الحَرْبِيِّ، وَنِصْفِهِ مِنْ الذِّمِّيِّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَمَا تَرَكُوهُ فَزَعًا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- أَوْ عَنْ مَيْتٍ وَلَا وَارِثَ لَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيْءٌ، وَمَصْرِفُهُ فِي مَصَالِحِ المُسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجُوزُ عَقْدُ الذِّمَّةِ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> لِمَنْ لَهُ كِتَابٌ أَوْ شُبْهَةُ كِتَابٍ كَالمَجُوسِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَلَا يَصِحُّ عَقْدُهَا إِلَّا مِنْ إِمَامٍ أَوْ نَائِبِهِ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَيَجِبُ:</span> إِنْ أَمِنَ مَكْرَهُمْ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالْتَزَمُوا لَنَا بِأَرْبَعَةِ أَحْكَامٍ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> أَنْ يُعْطُوا الجِزْيَةَ عَنْ يَدٍ وَهُمْ صَاغِرُونَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَأَلَّا يَذْكُرُوا دِينَ الإِسْلَامِ إِلَّا بِخَيْرٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَأَلَّا يَفْعَلُوا مَا فِيهِ ضَرَرٌ عَلَى المِسْلِمِينَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٤]</span> وَأَنْ تَجْرِيَ عَلَيْهِمْ أَحْكَامُ الإِسْلَامِ فِي:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- نَفْسٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>